config CCSDS_NET
	tristate "CCSDS virtual network interface (ccsdsnet + ccsdssim)"
	depends on INET
	help
	  Creates a virtual network interface "ccsdsnet" connected directly
	  to the IP layer (no Ethernet headers), paired with a character
	  device /dev/ccsdssim for injecting and extracting raw IP packets
	  from user space.

	  Useful for simulating CCSDS space links without real hardware.

	  To compile this driver as a loadable module, choose M here:
	  the module will be called ccsds.
